rc="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tortoiseknightma/blog/main/public/images/notion-migrated/site/home-banner.webp" alt="日本公演（海外）抽票流程" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></div></a></div><div class="notion-row"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="notion-bookmark notion-block-62b216903d154353a4b21fed2c27eafe" href="https://hackmd.io/@canaria/HkWlHe2jh"><div><div class="notion-bookmark-title">日本演唱會抽票攻略 - HackMD</div><div class="notion-bookmark-description">第一次去日本演唱會就上手!</div><div class="notion-bookmark-link"><div class="notion-bookmark-link-icon"><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tortoiseknightma/blog/main/public/images/notion-migrated/site/home-banner.webp" alt="日本演唱會抽票攻略 - HackMD" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></div><div class="notion-bookmark-link-text">https://hackmd.io/@canaria/HkWlHe2jh</div></div></div><div class="notion-bookmark-image"><img style="object-fit:cover" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tortoiseknightma/blog/main/public/images/notion-migrated/site/home-banner.webp" alt="日本演唱會抽票攻略 - HackMD" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></div></a></div><div class="notion-row"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="notion-bookmark notion-block-d45a3c9250094ac79d0331b846814bb5" href="https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Hinatazaka46/M.1697129120.A.AAE.html"><div><div class="notion-bookmark-title">Re: [閒聊] 關於購票方式的疑問</div><div class="notion-bookmark-description">我說的不一定正確，但是你參考看看，版上其他神人一堆 有錯還請指教 我個人從六月底公布有巡演後研究，從無到有自己摸索出來也成功看到現場演出了 所以我初參戰看到JOYFUL LOVE的彩虹真的在座位上哭出來，阿離題了sorry 回到你的問題，我的心得，想看日本演唱會 以我一個台灣base、沒日本親友、沒日本地址、又不想在蝦皮上找別人代抽的</div><div class="notion-bookmark-link"><div class="notion-bookmark-link-text">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Hinatazaka46/M.1697129120.A.AAE.html</div></div></div></a></div><div class="notion-row"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="notion-bookmark notion-block-f2a141f5140a4d5aae11cb8d54ce2cb0" href="https://www.tripvw.net/2023/11/JPconcert.html"><div><div class="notion-bookmark-title">日本演唱會FC抽票紀錄</div><